data.description: Price improvement! Charming chalet-style home nestled on 8.56 acres of serene wilderness, where wild horses roam freely. This private oasis offers a rare blend of rustic elegance and modern comfort. Big insulated shop. No CC&Rs. Step inside to find a cozy interior with tall wood-beamed ceilings. The river rock fireplace and heat pump will keep you at just the right temperature. With an abundance of natural light from skylights and windows. A spacious well-lit kitchen overlooks a gorgeous view. Upstairs, vaulted ceilings add an airy feel to the office and primary bedroom, providing a peaceful sanctuary. Well-maintained horse stalls and trails.  Lrg garden with greenhouses and fruit trees. Butts up to Weyerhauser land.
